t-size:12px;color:#64748b;\">7/2/2025</div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"font-weight:700;color:#10b981;\">+1 Certification</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 4px;\">\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-weight:700;\">Closed Deal – Omega - Welo Guard 1.0 New</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#64748b;\">6/1/2025</div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"font-weight:700;color:#10b981;\">+100 Closed/Won Dollars</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align:right;padding:8px 4px 12px;\">\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:12px;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;\">View All Transactions</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
